  "content_markdown": "Version: 8.0MarketingSales Creatio\nOn this page\nA lead is an interest in your products expressed by a potential customer. For example, new leads emerge if new users have registered on your website or if you receive a call from a contact who was previously interested in your services. With Creatio leads, you can work both with the customers who are ready to make a deal or those who need some more time to consider a purchase.\nIn Creatio, a lead can be created in the following ways:\n* added manually in the **Leads** section\n* [imported](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?product=base&ver=7&id=1252) from Excel\n* created automatically via registering on a [landing page](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1081).\nnote\nIf the **Create contact** checkbox is selected for a webpage in the \"Landings\" section, then when a consumer fills in the form of this landing, Creatio automatically creates a lead and a contact.\nUsing the Leads section, you can manage the lead nurturing process from the moment a potential customer expresses an interest in your products up to the handoff to sales.\nTo add a lead manually:\n1. Go to the **Leads** section.\n2. Click the **New Lead** button.\n3. Fill out the displayed mini page:\n1. **Customer need** field. The field is required.\n2. **Account name** field.\n3. **Contact name** field.\n4. **Email**.\n5. **Mobile phone** field.\nThe fields of the record can be populated later.\n4. Click the **Save** button to save the new folder (Fig. 1).\nFig. 1 Lead management process\n![Fig.\u00a01 Lead management process](https://academy.creatio.com/guides/sites/en/files/documentation/user/en/leads/BPMonlineHelp/leads_create/scr_create_new_lead.png)\nAs a result, a new record will be added to the **Leads** section.\n* * *\n## See also\u200b\n[Lead management process](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1767)\n[Lead duplicate search](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1865)\n[Predictive scoring of leads](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1863)\n[Leads FAQ](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1630)\n[Set up automatic lead registration from LinkedIn](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2368)\n[Set up automatic lead registration from social networks](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2477)\n* * *\n## Resources\u200b\n[Lead management](https://academy.creatio.com/node/531210/takecourse)",
